  <slide>
    <title>All Rules View</title>
    <contents>
      <figure>
        <img src="images/view-all-rules.png" role="none"/>
        <figcaption> AInspector screen shot of all rules view</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Shows how many rules have at least one violation, warning, or manual check, or if the rule passes.</li>
        <li>Warning rules are requirements that are important for accessibility, but not currently considered a requirement of WCAG.</li>
        <li>Rule Groupings:
          <ul>
            <li>Rule Category View</li>
            <li>WCAG Guidelines View</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>


  <slide>
    <title>Rule Group Result View</title>
    <contents>
      <figure>
        <img src="images/view-rule-group.png" role="none"/>
        <figcaption>AInspector screen shot of image rule group view</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Shows the rules that are included in the group and the overall evaluation result.</li>
        <li>Detailed information is available for the selected rule.</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>


  <slide>
    <title>Page, Website and Element Result View</title>
    <contents>

      <figure>
        <img src="images/view-rule.png" role="none"/>
        <figcaption>"AInspector screen shot of page, website and element results</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Shows the website, page and element results for a rule.</li>
        <li>Detailed information for each result is available for the selected result.</li>
        <li>The result can be highlighted on the page.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Detailed Result Information</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Rule Id</li>
        <li>Rule Definition</li>
        <li>Action</li>
        <li>Role</li>
        <li>Accessible Name</li>
        <li>Accessible Description</li>
        <li>Tag Name</li>
        <li>HTML Attributes</li>
        <li>ARIA Attributes</li>
        <li>Result Type</li>
      </ul>

    </contents>
  </slide>

