 <slide>
    <title>AInspector: Open-Source Code and Reporting Issues</title>
    <contents>

      <h2>Source Code</h2>
      <p>AInspector for WCAG Evaluation is open source software. The code is available at <a href="https://github.com/opena11y/ainspector">https://github.com/opena11y/ainspector</a>.</p>

      <h2>Reporting an Issue</h2>
      <p><a target="_github" href="https://github.com/opena11y/ainspector/issues">Create a github issue</a> or send me an e-mail: <a href="mailto:jongund@illinois.edu?subject=AInspector for WCAG issue">jongund@illinois.edu</a></p>

      <p>Ideally include a link to a page you found the problem and describe how I can replicate the issue.</p>

      <p>NOTE: AInspector for WCAG Evaluation is an open source project and users are very important in helping make the tool better.</p>

    </contents>
  </slide>


